name: LITTLE FLOATIES- NINONG
description:
ATTENTION: New creatures found! 

Tired of looking for your "Ninong" (Godfather) every Christmas? Worry no more coz I saw your Ninong hiding in the Planet Floaties and I brought him here for you. 

Planet Floaties is a Planet where there is no gravity and everyone is simply floating in the air, happy, and free.

-------------

This is my entry for Tezmas Pinoy Christmas Party-Themed NFT Making Contest. 

-------------

Collecting these creatures and all other works of Cherry Gum Studios will help support the dream world of a Filipino Artist to continue pursuing Art as a career.
